data.meta_description:
This is a questionnaire based on the viewing of a famous episode of CSI in Las Vegas entitled GRAVE DANGER. It was directed by Quentin Tarantino and it deals with Nick Stokes´s kidnapping.
You will also find a summary of the episode that the pupils will have to fill in thanks to the answers to the questionnaire. Finally, the last page consists in the keys.

CSI Grave Danger episode by Quentin Tarantino

This is a questionnaire based on the viewing of a famous episode of CSI in Las Vegas entitled GRAVE DANGER. It was directed by Quentin Tarantino and it deals with Nick Stokes´s kidnapping. You will also find a summary of the episode that the pupils will have to fill in thanks to the answers to the questionnaire. Finally, the last page consists in the keys.
